Welcome to a whole new world of TV. These features will allow you to discover and engage with new channels movies and TV shows in an all new exciting way. Check them out on your iPhone iPad or Apple TV. Tuned for Content Discovery Live TV: Drop in to 250 channels streaming the latest movies binge worthy TV shows breaking news live sports and more. On Demand: Watch hit movies like Big Fish Zodiac Legally Blonde The Big Short and more anytime you want with Pluto TV on demand. What s New New Interface: Pluto TV is always on. Our new and improved channel lineup shows you the entire universe of Pluto TV s movies and TV shows in an easy to navigate channel guide and on demand menu. Channel Favoriting: Is it a mystery trying to find the Unsolved Mysteries channel Tag your fave channels to keep them at the top of your channel guide every time you watch Pluto TV. Add to Watch List Watch Now: See something you love on one of our 250 channels We re not surprised. If your title is available on demand you ll see the Watch Now button pop up in the guide. Click that to watch it on demand. Genre Category Navigator: Find what you love even faster. Choose from categories like Movies News Entertainment Sports and more to skip directly through Pluto TV s 250 channels to the channels you love the most. More features are coming soon! Onwards and upwards!

If you re having binge watching problems we feel bad for you son. We have 99 episodes of ALF and you don t have to pay for any of them. Yes we added support for full TV Series On Demand. Now you can watch Thousands of your favorite shows and navigate easily between seasons. We also added support for iOS 11 because it would be pretty silly if we didn t. We also fixed like 4 little bugs that our QA guy Arvin found. Email his boss Mary pluto.tv if you find anymore bugs or if you just want to talk about stuff.
We added support to increase our Free On Demand Movies catalog. Now there are more movies to choose from. We also fixed an issue where longer movie titles were getting cut off.

We made it easier to hide the channels you don t want to watch. We get it...maybe the Horror 24 7 channel is just too scary or the Food TV channel makes you sooo hungry that you re not sticking with your diet. Whatever the case inside the My Pluto tab there is a 1 click tap to hide those channels from showing up on the guide. We also made a few bug fixes. Yes that s a pretty vague description but it s fairly boring stuff for 99 of you reading this. For example one of the APIs was taking a few milliseconds too long to fire and there was a very rare case where iPad users would see their app crash if they ferociously switched back and forth between portrait and landscape modes like a crazy person.

Are you sitting in bed with your iPad and just can t muster enough energy to turn your screen sideways Don t worry we ve got you covered. Just tap on the guide button to bring up all 100 channels to see what s on. Still nothing that tickles your fancy after scrolling through every channel Really We ll you better check out the New On Demand section. We ve completely updated the movies and made it easier to find the top hits. Did the last build make your app crash after opening a push notification Yes that was terrible and we sent that engineer to detention. Our new engineer fixed the issues and she promises this build won t do that anymore.

New Guide More Channels and Next Level Performance...We took this baby down to the studs. Speaking of amazing remodels you ll notice we added Frontdoor CH 615 a DIY channel with series from HGTV. On Demand you say Free on demand Your wish is our command. Watch thousands of hit movies and binge worthy TV shows whenever and wherever you want. When your selection is over switch back to live TV to see what s on. This new version clearly answers a burning question from all of our users do you really have live sports breaking news hit movie channels music cartoons and crazy eccentric channels like The High Channel cough and Anime we re nerds too . Yes the answer is YES. Have more questions about our Pluto TV s 100 live channels or 1000 s of movies and TV shows on demand Contact our office mom mary pluto.tv and she will fix you right up. Also and I promise this is the last point we need your help! Tell us what movies TV shows or internet series you want us to add to Pluto TV. Mary pluto.tv also handles those requests. Okay...one more but this is a pro tip not a point. If you access the My Pluto section and customize your guide so only the cool channels show up...you may or may not improve your television watching experience. That s really up to you!
